Instructions:
First we gotta create clevercloud/maven.json inside our project root and add following:

{
  "deploy": {
    "goal": "yourgoal"
  }
}

Second we gotta git push the project
Third we gotta create an application on clevercloud and
IMPORANT-> Inside environment table we shall add this changes:

CC_JAVA_VERSION="17"
LIBXML_VERSION="2.11.7"
LIBXSLT_VERSION="1.1.39"
MAVEN_DEPLOY_GOAL="spring-boot:run"

